This set includes all 10 episodes of the British sketch-variety show from 1972-1974. Backed by Benny's half-dressed flock of frisky foxes and a quick-witted team of entertainers, the show makes a mockery of anything and everything, and ...    Full Description, and made the world giggle and guffaw in 140 languages. Special features include Biography series episode, trivia quiz, interactive menus, and scene selection.
